Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:22.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清风　云彩　仰望群星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:30.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中的悸动　如波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:38.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无穷　无尽　战火连绵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:46.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等扬帆　即日踏上征途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:53.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有暗阎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:01:01.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻塞前行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:13.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥想　祈福　唯愿君平安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:28.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0}向无尽宇宙{\fsp-9}、{\fsp1.5}出征
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:07.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:28.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:39.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:01.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之剑{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斩断这一昏暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:08.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的要塞落于敌手 臣愧对殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1110,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1110,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臣力排众议 一力承担的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却落得如此下场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣甘愿领罚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}无地藩王 亚术曼·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}無地藩王 アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,923)\fad(500,500)}亚历亚伯特·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军驻留部队仅有区区三百艘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方十倍于我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以少胜多的先例并不少见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我方太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来 大家都有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众卿好像误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事对泰坦尼亚有益无害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海贼此后的动向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海贼们数量愈增愈多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在要塞周围集结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总数恐怕不下五千艘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏他们能聚集这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若聚成集团 倒也不可小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此举无疑于自掘坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好趁此良机一举斩断祸根 去除后患
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请允许我将功补过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命你作为副司令辅佐哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(571,290)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}两场邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星卡嘉诺特 流星旗军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星カガノート 流星旗軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星旗军也蛮能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能行得通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给还顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1403,923)\fad(500,500)}米兰达·卡西米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1403,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横看竖看 这艘船还是这么老
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏它还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保养得好 船长的技术也没得说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为方修利提督的座驾还略嫌不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,923)\fad(500,500)}道尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}}ドールマン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话 就准备最新型的舰只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我想向提督引荐几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1116,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1116,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能劳您大驾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是原提兰基亚军的汉力克少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(855,923)\fad(500,500)}汉力克少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(855,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヘンリック少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜见凯贝罗斯会战英雄的尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(552,923)\fad(500,500)}托斯卡尼少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}トスカーニ少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,923)\fad(500,500)}马凯泽中将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}マッケンゼン中将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马凯泽中将和托斯卡尼少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起来都不怎么像海贼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几位都是正统军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为个中原因 不便透漏国家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特意当逃兵 真辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么憎恨泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军怎么会帮海贼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督说得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会重蹈艾里亚和提兰基亚的覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何根据？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们攻占要塞后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军正源源赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其数可达五千艘以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有方修利提督率军 岂不是所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里人才济济 根本轮不到我出场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了振奋士气 英雄是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请和我们携手 再次击破泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意下如何 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是大舰队的总司令耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘心永远坐着那艘破船航行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船破了点 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候能完成补给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有流星旗军在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就不用东躲西藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是五千艘耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是连泰坦尼亚的要塞都打下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蝇这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若一只只解决根本没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们若全部聚集到一处呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾宾格王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 那艘船是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是泰坦尼亚的军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是从要塞逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾宾格王国 第二公主莉迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是泰坦尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然逃到我国…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们赶走不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们有伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下也思量再三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是同意他们入境了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若私藏泰坦尼亚军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被流星旗军盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是个区区海贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 他们攻陷了泰坦尼亚要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其势头不可小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说现在支配这片星域的是他们也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泰坦尼亚也不会坐视不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷比起泰坦尼亚更怕海贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题我很难回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为父皇是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥舰队旗舰 台风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ艦隊旗艦 タイフーン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是将讨厌的苍蝇一网打尽的绝佳良机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请诸位全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说藩王殿下为什么要指派我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(803,803)\fad(500,500)\fs40}Uraniberg
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,878)\fad(500,500)}天城 休憩圆顶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(727,918)\fad(500,500)\fs31\fnms gothic}ウラニボルグ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,988)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}天の城 ラウンジドーム
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,论率兵打仗 应该是你比较在行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若由我担任副将 哲力胥会束手束脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿还有近卫军司令的任务在身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下有请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行多半能解开你心头的疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗 前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道艾斯特拉德·泰坦尼亚侯爵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是殿下的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现任维尔达纳帝国军务大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正阴谋把我从藩王宝座上赶下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多半是破坏我族团结的流言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不可小视
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿似乎极为肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他会无中生有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔纳达的宫廷贵族若要作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然会怂恿艾斯特拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我 就会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若平白无故地处分军务大臣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会让亲者痛 仇者快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯特拉德阁下可是泰坦尼亚的重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让鼠辈们高兴两天也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下 那可…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不需要马上动手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当前只需防止伤口扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗卿听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤命你带法尔密子爵为高级副官共赴战场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军务大臣的公子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他挟做人质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿收法尔密子爵为我的高级副官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜牺牲自己的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要将帝国内的敌人一扫而光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一决断听来有些悲壮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是哥哥没有取代弟弟的资格…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下就是本次受命担任阁下副官的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1313,855)\fad(500,500)}法尔密·泰坦尼亚子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1313,925)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー・タイタニア子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 法尔密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问我该如何称呼您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵阁下 还是上将阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该叫你子爵阁下 不 准将阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请您不要这样称呼我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我褚士朗卿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必拘于礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕在下冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓副官应当做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐军总司令是哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他强到没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用我出场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿只是为褚士朗卿垫场的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来法尔密卿喜欢挑拨离间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你如此之高的评价 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队正在准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去晨曦女神等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙兰西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 褚士朗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1065,923)\fad(500,500)}芙兰西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1065,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}フランシア
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来大家都有些高估我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌我双方都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几个国家不愿加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾宾格王国还藏有泰坦尼亚的逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攘外必先安内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要派兵前往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种穷国 下官三两下就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚有所行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰艇一万两千艘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官似乎是哲力胥·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量是我军的一倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 若是猛将哲力胥带兵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其破坏力会加成数倍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以少胜多的战例数不胜数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们还有方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军风头正劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上方修利提督运筹帷幄…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得马上把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个一心想逃的男人能有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们在就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little-big-horn要塞在天城建成以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可列入三大巨型建筑物之列
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是重要文化遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 这一要塞也是泰坦尼亚的重要军事据点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥的目的必然是夺回要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们布阵时就以此为盾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全员困守要塞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这样背临要塞布下密集阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们生怕伤到要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击时难免畏首畏尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机一到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由别动队将其一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的刺猬战术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们占有地利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是哲力胥 我们也不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当方修利没来过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌方据点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人似乎打算负隅顽抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚开始进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按作战计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰径直前行 不准减速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 要塞会被打得千疮百孔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我们重要的军事据点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞被夺乃泰坦尼亚之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能借此将苍蝇一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一两个要塞算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军并未减速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军一并向这边冲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Point Z02和M62
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派第一第三分队前去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队 二十秒内到达要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全军下令 作战计划有变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把马凯泽给我叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战舰斯凯拉 失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马凯泽提督也战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马凯泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战舰特塞斯被击沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉力克少将战死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托斯卡尼舰队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队冲过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哲力胥阁下请降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真符合哲力胥卿的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有我出场的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想会会你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道咱们还能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1265,923)\fad(500,500)}李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1265,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ドクター・リー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 还能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星旗军似乎全军覆灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让他们不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 我们算是捡了一条命咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是你能拿这条命做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若拿来虚度时光的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没什么意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌泰坦尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚是全宇宙最为强大的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已 泰坦尼亚没有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为自己能灭亡泰坦尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今后可能会出现转机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近发生了几件前所未有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚四公爵之一不可能被一国舰队打败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座的这位完成了这一壮举
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以认为你是在表扬我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在贬低泰坦尼亚罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能性还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇泰坦尼亚霸权的变革之浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个天才 我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 能受到李博士这么高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人真有这么大的价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督个人没有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所持有的变革可能性才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督恨泰坦尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,923)\fad(500,500)}艾宾格王国国王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国国王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什么烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇的判断没有错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚没有怪罪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚要我国将能量矿山交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以示忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去那座矿山的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个国家都会破产的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在考验我们的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法违逆泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如此一来 百姓的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要证明我们别无二心就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我 莉迪亚去当人质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想去天城玩玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可… 公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想见见传说中的四公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一股微不足道的新风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它将为泰坦尼亚注入全新的某物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣听说天城是个可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主真是太勇敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 爷爷我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}微小的新风


